headline.main: After Kansas Shooting, a Community in Fear
headline.print_headline: After Kansas Shooting, a Community in Fear

lead_paragraph: The Syrian opposition has provisionally accepted 12 principles given to delegates by the United Nations at the end of an eight-day round of peace talks, chief negotiator Nasr al-Hariri said.
